data.description:
This property offers a perfect blend of practical features and aesthetic appeal, making it a standout choice in the Florence Gardens
community. Enjoy the convenience and privacy of a split floor plan, and take advantage of the attached storage/workshop space, Embrace the Arizona
sunshine on the screened-in porch, a perfect spot for enjoying the outdoors. Revel in the beauty of a beautifully remodeled interior, showcasing a bright and
modern style.
